  "description": "OVERDUB as the surface signal — tape-warm, dub groove — with OCEANDEEP as its deep-pressure shadow. OVERDUB plays what is heard above the thermocline; OCEANDEEP shapes what exists beneath it. The coupling carries the brightness envelope from OVERDUB's filter down into OCEANDEEP's hydrostatic compressor.",
