    "retreat": "OVERDUB — Temporal Evolution and Degradation-as-Architecture",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-21",
    "scripture": ["Scripture VII-2: The Echo Serves the Silence"],
    "revelation": "The dub signal and the ocean deep signal are the same note at two depths — the high pressure changes the timbre but not the intention.",
    "diagnosis": "Acetate Abyss is an Entangled preset pairing OVERDUB's tape character with OCEANDEEP's Darkness Filter Ceiling (B031). When OVERDUB's filter opens on a hard hit, the brightness coupling feeds OCEANDEEP's exciter, briefly lifting the abyss ceiling."
  },
